Executive Profile
Edgar H. Lawton IIIPresident and Treasurer, Hartsville Oil Mill, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.56--
Background

		Mr. Edgar H. Lawton, III, has been the President and Treasurer of Hartsville Oil Mill, Inc. since 2000. Mr. Lawton served as Vice President of Hartsville Oil Mill from 1991 to 2000. He has been a Director of Hartsville Oil Mill, Inc. since 1991. He served as an Independent Director of Sonoco Products Company from 2001 to July 18, 2017.	
	



